y to Friday is £14.99<br\/>The saturday delivery is £29.99<br\/>The sunday delivery is £34.99<\/p>","highlight_effect":"underline","text_transform":"none"}},"collapsible_tab_UL3rrw":{"type":"collapsible_tab","settings":{"open_by_default":false,"icon":"none","another_icon":"","use_secondary_background":false,"heading":"Flexible Delivery","tab_content":"<p>We know that you expect your goods to be delivered promptly and efficiently. That’s why we have made it a priority at electricshop.com to deliver your goods as quickly as possible using our fast, efficient delivery service which comes direct to your home and is FREE for most items!<br\/><br\/>- We deliver seven days a week <br\/>- Standard deliveries are despatched via specialist carriers and are normally delivered within 3-5 working days. <br\/>- Express deliveries are dispatched same day (if ordered before 14:30) for delivery within 1-2 working days.<br\/>- For weekend deliveries, orders need to be placed by 14:30 on Friday.<br\/>- Larger Items are despatched using our team of specialist nationwide carriers. You will be contacted within 48 hours verifying your order and an estimated delivery date.<br\/>- Deliveries direct from manufacturers or suppliers can take a little longer but we will keep you informed and updated.<\/p>","highlight_effect":"underline","text_transform":"none"}},"social_sharing":{"type":"social_sharing","settings":{}}},"block_order":["labels_and_badges_Eiedzj","vendor","product_title","space_KKnHzV","rating_J9ax4R","identifier","price","text_PLkYLp","text_with_icon_4NbixV","separator_nUa9hN","variant_picker","inventory_status_8LgeE4","buy_buttons","text_with_icon_K46hgt","text_with_icon_7YaxUe","text_with_icon_NaTmBK","estimate_delivery_MTTqQU","text_with_icon_1","text_with_icon_2","text_with_icon_3","text_with_icon_4","description_7pUwRw","text_VTYVwf","space_mUrayz","collapsible_tab_1","collapsible_tab_HXkwRD","collapsible_tab_2","collapsible_tab_T83VWR","collapsible_tab_UL3rrw","social_sharing"],"settings":{"enable_sticky_content":true,"make_content_center":false,"desktop_media_width":"large","media_ratio":"16\/9","show_media_with_variant_selected":false,"option_to_classify_variant_media":"","zoom_effect":"magnifier","enable_video_autoplay":true,"enable_microdata":false,"show_breadcrumbs":true,"sticky_add_to_cart_style":"bottom_bar","sticky_add_to_cart_show_quantity":false,"section_width":"full-width","padding_top":16,"padding_bottom":0,"show_section_divider":false}},"product_details_Hp67jL":{"type":"product-details","blocks":{"highlight_feature_GpV4tD":{"type":"highlight_feature","settings":{"icon":"quality","another_icon":"","heading":"Flattering fit","heading_size":"large","text":"<p>Enjoy the flattering fit and butterfly soft feeling<\/p>","desktop_content_alignment":"center","mobile_content_alignment":"center","highlight_effect":"underline","text_transform":"none"}},"highlight_feature_Npkm4f":{"type":"highlight_feature","settings":{"icon":"quality","another_icon":"","heading":"Flattering fit","heading_size":"large","text":"<p>Enjoy the flattering fit and butterfly soft feeling<\/p>","desktop_content_alignment":"center","mobile_content_alignment":"center","highlight_effect":"underline","text_transform":"none"}},"description_phHN9L":{"type":"description","settings":{"heading":"","heading_size":"large","heading_alignment":"left","number_of_lines_shown":"none","read_more_label":"Read more","see_less_label":"See less"}},"rich_text_WxhdWa":{"type":"rich_text","disabled":true,"settings":{"icon":"none","another_icon":"","heading":"Compact and powerful: The JAZ Wizard 5 speaker is the right companion for your music.","heading_size":"large","text":"<p><strong>AT HOME AND OUTDOORS<\/strong><br\/><br\/>The Wizard 5 wireless speaker is great for any use, not only in the home but also for an excursion or outing. Its compact size, minimalist design and LED that follows the rhythm of music make it a pleasant and adaptable object for the home. The 5W power is great for use in the home whether you want to listen to music after a long day at work or watch a film on your laptop. With its practical integrated strap, you can attach the speaker to a backpack and take it to the park on a sunny spring day.<br\/><br\/><br\/><strong>HIGH-PERFORMANCE BATTERY<br\/><br\/><\/strong>The 1200 mAh battery, when fully charged, is suitable for up to 6 hours of active use and 24 hours standby This means you can listen to music for a long time even if you are away from home during the day for a trip to the lake or the mountains. When the speaker is out of power, simply lift the integrated strap to find the power socket. Connect it to a power source with a USB port using the included Micro-USB cable.<br\/><br\/><br\/><strong>REMOTE OPERATION<br\/><br\/><\/strong>Thanks to the range of up to 10 metres, you can leave your device in another room or in your pocket without any signal interruption. What’s more, this wireless speaker has two volume control buttons so you can decide how loud you want the sound to be even if you don’t have your smartphone, tablet or laptop near you.<\/p>","text_alignment":"left","highlight_effect":"underline","text_transform":"none","select_page":"","number_of_lines_shown":"none","read_more_label":"Read more","see_less_label":"See less","show_payment_icons":false,"payment_icon":"","show_border":false,"color_scheme_light":"scheme-1","color_scheme_dark":"scheme-2"}},"specifications_WqUq9M":{"type":"specifications","settings":{"heading":"Key Features","heading_size":"large","text":"<p>Bring home the<strong> QE65S90FATXXU<\/strong> and experience cinema-quality visuals, immersive sound, and next-gen AI enhancements – all in an elegant, slim design built for the future of home entertainment.<\/p><ul><li>NQ4 AI Gen3 Processor with 128 neural networks<\/li><li>4K AI Upscaling Pro for sharper detail<\/li><li>OLED HDR+ for breathtaking brightness and depth<\/li><li>AI Motion Enhancer Pro for smooth, clear action<\/li><li>Dolby Atmos® immersive surround sound<\/li><li>Ultra-slim LaserSlim design with minimal bezels<\/li><li>Object Tracking Sound for realistic sound placement<\/li><li>Motion Xcelerator 144Hz with VRR\/4K@120Hz support<\/li><li>Pantone® Validated colour accuracy<\/li><\/ul>","text_alignment":"left","table_detail":"<p><em><strong>Features<\/strong><\/em>: custom.type<br\/>- Speakers: 2.1CH<br\/>- Type of Antenna: Terrestrial & Satellite<br\/>- USB Recording: Yes<\/p><p><em><strong>Design Elements<\/strong><\/em><br\/>- Colour: Graphite Black<br\/>- Colour Group: Black<\/p><p><em><strong>Connectivity<\/strong><\/em><br\/>- Bluetooth:Yes<br\/>- HDMI:Yes<br\/>- Number of HDMI Ports:4<br\/>- Number of USB Ports:2<br\/>- Smart Connect:Yes<br\/>- Smart TV:Yes<br\/>- USB:Yes<br\/>- Wi-Fi:Yes<\/p><p><em><strong>Dimensions & Weight<\/strong><\/em><br\/>- Depth:3.99 cm<br\/>- Depth with Stand:26.52 cm<br\/>- Height:83.17 cm<br\/>- Height with Stand:89.67 cm<br\/>- Shipping Depth:16 cm<br\/>- Shipping Height:95 cm<br\/>- Shipping Weight:29.9 kg<br\/>- Shipping Width:151.7 cm<br\/>- Weight:21.2 kg<br\/>- Width:144.43 cm<br\/>- Width with Stand:144.43 cm<\/p>","text_empty_fields":"-","row_shown_by_default":4,"view_more_button":"Read more","view_less_button":"See less"}},"rich_text_aRHDWE":{"type":"rich_text","settings":{"icon":"authentic","another_icon":"","heading":"Authencity Guaranteed","heading_size":"medium","text":"<p>We only sell authentic products from verified brand partners and retail partners globally.<\/p>","text_alignment":"left","highlight_effect":"underline","text_transform":"none","select_page":"","number_of_lines_shown":"none","read_more_label":"Read more","see_less_label":"See less","show_payment_icons":true,"payment_icon":"visa , master , diners_club , paypal , american_express","show_border":true,"color_scheme_light":"","color_scheme_dark":""}}},"block_order":["highlight_feature_GpV4tD","highlight_feature_Npkm4f","description_phHN9L","rich_text_WxhdWa","specifications_WqU